---
---

<!-- FAQ -->
<section id="faq" class="py-24 bg-slate-50 border-t border-slate-200">
	<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
		<div class="text-center mb-16">
			<h2 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 tracking-tight mb-4">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
			<p class="text-lg text-slate-600">Everything you need to know about Pressly.</p>
		</div>
		
		<div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
			<!-- FAQ 1 -->
			<details name="pressly-faq" class="group bg-white rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 overflow-hidden shadow-sm" open>
				<summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-bold cursor-pointer list-none p-6 text-slate-900 text-lg hover:bg-slate-50 transition-colors">
					<span>What services are available?</span>
					<span class="transition group-open:rotate-180 text-primary">
						<svg fill="none" height="24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path></svg>
					</span>
				</summary>
				<div class="text-slate-600 px-6 pb-6 pt-2 leading-relaxed border-t border-slate-100">
					We currently offer premium ironing services for all types of clothing. You can select standard daily wear, heavy garments, or delicate fabrics when placing your order.
				</div>
			</details>
			
			<!-- FAQ 2 -->
			<details name="pressly-faq" class="group bg-white rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 overflow-hidden shadow-sm">
				<summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-bold cursor-pointer list-none p-6 text-slate-900 text-lg hover:bg-slate-50 transition-colors">
					<span>How does pricing work?</span>
					<span class="transition group-open:rotate-180 text-primary">
						<svg fill="none" height="24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path></svg>
					</span>
				</summary>
				<div class="text-slate-600 px-6 pb-6 pt-2 leading-relaxed border-t border-slate-100">
					Pricing is transparent and based on a per-item rate set by the vendor you choose. You will see an estimated cost before booking, and the final price is confirmed once items are collected.
				</div>
			</details>

			<!-- FAQ 3 -->
			<details name="pressly-faq" class="group bg-white rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 overflow-hidden shadow-sm">
				<summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-bold cursor-pointer list-none p-6 text-slate-900 text-lg hover:bg-slate-50 transition-colors">
					<span>Who picks clothes?</span>
					<span class="transition group-open:rotate-180 text-primary">
						<svg fill="none" height="24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path></svg>
					</span>
				</summary>
				<div class="text-slate-600 px-6 pb-6 pt-2 leading-relaxed border-t border-slate-100">
					The verified vendor you select (or the one we assign if you choose auto-assignment) will personally collect the clothes from your doorstep at your scheduled time.
				</div>
			</details>

			<!-- FAQ 4 -->
			<details name="pressly-faq" class="group bg-white rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 overflow-hidden shadow-sm">
				<summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-bold cursor-pointer list-none p-6 text-slate-900 text-lg hover:bg-slate-50 transition-colors">
					<span>Can I cancel?</span>
					<span class="transition group-open:rotate-180 text-primary">
						<svg fill="none" height="24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path></svg>
					</span>
				</summary>
				<div class="text-slate-600 px-6 pb-6 pt-2 leading-relaxed border-t border-slate-100">
					Yes, you can cancel your booking for free any time before the vendor starts the pickup trip. Once the vendor is on the way, a small cancellation fee may apply.
				</div>
			</details>
			
			<!-- FAQ 5 -->
			<details name="pressly-faq" class="group bg-white rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 overflow-hidden shadow-sm">
				<summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-bold cursor-pointer list-none p-6 text-slate-900 text-lg hover:bg-slate-50 transition-colors">
					<span>How payments work?</span>
					<span class="transition group-open:rotate-180 text-primary">
						<svg fill="none" height="24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path></svg>
					</span>
				</summary>
				<div class="text-slate-600 px-6 pb-6 pt-2 leading-relaxed border-t border-slate-100">
					You can pay securely via the app using UPI, cards, or net banking upon delivery. Cash on delivery is also accepted by most vendors.
				</div>
			</details>
			
			<!-- FAQ 6 -->
			<details name="pressly-faq" class="group bg-white rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 overflow-hidden shadow-sm">
				<summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-bold cursor-pointer list-none p-6 text-slate-900 text-lg hover:bg-slate-50 transition-colors">
					<span>How vendors are selected?</span>
					<span class="transition group-open:rotate-180 text-primary">
						<svg fill="none" height="24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path></svg>
					</span>
				</summary>
				<div class="text-slate-600 px-6 pb-6 pt-2 leading-relaxed border-t border-slate-100">
					Every vendor on Pressly goes through a rigorous verification process. We check their setup, quality of work, and reliability before they are allowed to accept orders on our platform.
				</div>
			</details>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
